{"tid":531284,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"癡線佬是如何鍊成","createTime":"2018-01-16T15:27:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-17T01:06:57.000Z","uid":68626,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"282ec89a91de483bfcaa0d970dab5d5f17f2dbc7","tid":531284,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T15:27:33.000Z","msg":"每一個自殺而死去既亡者<br />\n或者係變態殺人犯<br />\n心中都有巨大既怨恨<br />\n分別可能只係殺人犯揀左去發泄<br />\n自殺既揀左去逃避<br />\n最近我發現唔少身邊既人唔開心既個陣<br />\n都會想搵人傾訴<br />\n但係其實搵人傾訴通常都會令到你既怨恨更加嚴重<br />\n因為會覺得身邊無人明白你<br />\n甚至覺得<br />\n你地班撚樣唔係成日話唔開心搵人傾嫁咩?<br />\n屌那星無人SHOW我呀<br />\n之後就慢慢變成心理變態<br />\n點睇?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"656ac2169ab55ace99e08fcad849ac3f937ef867","tid":531284,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T15:29:13.000Z","msg":"童年陰影係主因"},{"pid":"a1380d1a42e73d82f4c9e6a5af5d7a5d14ef4aee","tid":531284,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"656ac2169ab55ace99e08fcad849ac3f937ef867","tid":531284,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T15:29:13.000Z","msg":"童年陰影係主因"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T15:31:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f867566122e5690cdbb621bcf94e015db1d75f82","tid":531284,"uid":74262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T15:33:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fffc0b033751e52932dfd5c7b5a9fe45db941aeb","tid":531284,"uid":165024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T15:36:09.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecbcc67a9dcd4b981bd1039aeebab7c0ec35d1ed","tid":531284,"uid":150611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T01:06:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}